47:1 COMMENT "# Generic type dissection: match on a generic type parameter to"
47:64 EOL "\n"
48:1 COMMENT "# select code paths at compile time. During monomorphisation, the"
48:66 EOL "\n"
49:1 COMMENT "# concrete type is known and only the matching arm survives."
49:61 EOL "\n"
50:1 COMMENT "# See doc/spec.html for a class method example."
50:48 EOL "\n"
51:1 EOL "\n"
